Welcome to the fruit game! Here you will meet (and possibly eat):
The green apple.
The blueberry.
The dark red cherry.

> x table
It's a sturdy wooden table. There seems to be something on it.

> search table
On the wooden table you find a green apple, a blueberry, and a dark red cherry.

> eat berry
Did you want to eat the blueberry or the dark red cherry?

> blueberry
You eat the blueberry.

> take cherry
You can't take the dark red cherry.

>
